             <img alt="Takeisha Smith" class="img-responsive" height="768" src="https://career.uncc.edu/sites/career.uncc.edu/files/styles/flexslider_full/public/fields/success-story/field_photo/takeisha-smith.jpg?itok=terb9oBS" title="Takeisha Smith" width="1024"/>
            </div>
            <div class="right-container">
             <h2>
              Takeisha Smith
             </h2>
             <em>
              Major: Political Science
             </em>
             <br/>
             <p>
              I signed up through Hire-A-Niner with Enterprise. My mock interview went great. I received great feedback from Ms. Chelsey on how I can improve marketing myself and she also gave me the option of a possible job with the company.
             </p>
